@page "/"
@page "/Default"
<PageTitle>Welcome</PageTitle>

<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Wingtip Toys</h1>
    <h2>Wingtip Toys can help you find the perfect gift.</h2>
    <p class="lead">We're all about transportation toys. You can order any of our toys today. Each toy listing has detailed information to help you choose the right toy.</p>
    <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/ProductList">Browse Products</a></p>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>Cars, planes, boats, and more</h3>
        <p>Explore the complete Wingtip catalog with the same familiar markup migrated to Blazor.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>Detailed product pages</h3>
        <p>Every toy has a product details page with pricing, images, and fast add-to-cart links.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>Shopping cart workflow</h3>
        <p>Update quantities, remove products, and continue shopping without losing your cart.</p>
    </div>
</div>

